| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2411 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f50b527d-bb1d-5efd-87df-4cf899ffe5fd"
